title: Portable Sys Tracer 1.6.0.16
description:
SysTracer is a system utility application that analyzes your PC for modified files, folders or registry entries. You have the possibility to take an unlimited number of snapshots, at any time you want.

Information related to your files, folders and registry entries is stored in snapshot files for later analysis. You can create as many snapshots you may want.If you want to see the differences between your system status at two different moments in time simply compare the snapshots you made at these points.
